fe-of-ice-officer-who-shot-and-killed-colombian-man-in-maine-says-he-asked-her-to-lie-about-his-character-to-tell-everyone-that-he-was-a-good-person/articleshow/132466738.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-17T23:02:47+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132466952,imgsize-56000.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Meet Chelsie Anderson: American woman who accidentally became a Mexican drug cartel queen]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132460875.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Chelsie Anderson went from serving tables to becoming a pivotal figure in drug trafficking. After her marriage fell apart, she linked up with a global cartel and quickly escalated within their ranks, overseeing substantial drug shipments each week. Eventually, she emerged as a key leader in an international drug ring, underscoring the intricate web of criminal operations and the people involved.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/meet-chelsie-anderson-american-mom-of-two-who-accidentally-became-a-mexican-drug-cartel-queen/articleshow/132460875.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/meet-chelsie-anderson-american-mom-of-two-who-accidentally-became-a-mexican-drug-cartel-queen/articleshow/132460875.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-17T23:53:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132460893,imgsize-105970.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘This will offend a lot of people’: New UK PM Andy Burnham's tea-making habit sparks debate]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatim